23:02.000 --> 23:05.000
These light particles became known as photons,

23:05.000 --> 23:09.000
and this quantum theory explained previously confusing phenomena,

23:09.000 --> 23:14.000
like black body radiation or why hot objects glow the way they do.

23:14.000 --> 23:21.000
And the photoelectric effect, or why light can liberate electrons from metallic surfaces in the way that it does.

23:21.000 --> 23:26.000
